GOAT 🐐⚽️🥅🇦🇷 @leomessi …
I haven’t rooted this hard for a player in a long time. I feel absolutely exhausted after watching arguably the best World Cup Final in history, which was made even better by Lionel Messi achieving “the impossible dream”. A Storybook international ending for one of, if not THE, the greatest soccer (football haha) player in history. Congratulations Messi. Incredibly happy for you and your soccer legacy. 
#worldcup #argentina #lionelmessi

Happy Father’s Day to all my fellow dads (& future dads, uncles, and dude influences). Now, you may not be the “Best Dad By Par”, since my family has let me know I’ve already claimed that title with this t-shirt, but I know you’re still awesome and hugely important in others’ lives. 
And sending so much love and appreciation to my own dad, whose example of love, humor, responsibility, service, and faith has helped shape and influence me into the father that I am today.
#happyfathersday

Obligatory “birthday” post!..🎉
with bed head and breakfast made by my wonderful wife (the breakfast, not the bed head…)
You can check out my Stories for more bday…
Hard to believe another year has passed. I’ve been pondering on my life experiences as this birthday in particular approached. I am so grateful for my family, and for you my friends, both new and old, and all of the fantastic memories we’ve made. 
Thank you for your love and friendship. ❤️
Here’s to another round of years to make many more! 🙌🏻

STRIKE OVER! 🎉Tentative agreement reached for @sagaftra 🙌🏻🙌🏻

Now let’s get to work! 💪🏻
